{"tid":608970,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[麻雀撚]一人一個遇過牌品最差既人","createTime":"2018-03-28T15:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T16:35:08.000Z","uid":67976,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4674581a5a31cb5ed4710ea9e922aa027e911781","tid":608970,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"都幾耐之前既事<br />\n<br />\n條友打足咁耐屌足咁耐 食佢兩鋪十番就鬼剎咁嘈  又極易燥底 明明只係打緊10/128 笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中間我自摸左幾鋪四五番 佢又係咁嘈我話阻佢做大牌 話我趕盡殺絕 我就話咁你打乜撚野三番起姐 打八鋪起你鋪鋪都可以做大牌 佢淨係話我再做三四番就埋數走人<br />\n<br />\n之後我自摸兩鋪八九番 佢就話咁咪係囉 我輸得起 前提係你要做大牌 我心諗盲既都睇得出你係輸錢唔gur想攞尾彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />輸得起就唔係咁既樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好笑係佢燥就越出沖 越出沖就越燥 越燥就越出沖 當佢提款機咁禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係未見過一個廿歲出頭既人既牌品可以咁撚差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我相信呢度有唔少人同佢打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c6228165a9ece5c8cce40c31d4221f9ca12f83","tid":608970,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f9c42b2059ae6012c39de300e06cfe14a67918","tid":608970,"uid":77022,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"CHING 係TG Group 約打麻雀架？"},{"pid":"b998b90f7cf3f376f8c68ec6ae73598f75fae384","tid":608970,"uid":134694,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"試過同中學同學打<br />\n佢一開嬴少少開始不斷教人打<br />\n邊家出沖又係到話唔應該打呢隻<br />\n成場無停過口<br />\n佢又真係勁多自摸<br />\n可以人地打出唔食,下ROUND就自摸<br />\n我地幾家已經不斷輸錢<br />\n仲要俾佢炎煩足成場<